rule-4-2-a.test_description: Baseline and Proposed building have one building segment and  one zone with matching minimum humidity schedules. Expected result: PASS

standard.rule_description: Humidity Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.

rule-4-2-b.test_description: Baseline and Proposed building have one building segment and  one zone with non-matching minimum humidity  schedules. Expected result: UNDETERMINED

standard.rule_description: Humidity Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.

rule-4-2-c.test_description: Baseline and Proposed building have one building segment and  one zone. Neither have minimum humidity schedules. Expected result: PASS

standard.rule_description: Humidity Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.

rule-4-2-d.test_description: Baseline and Proposed building have one building segment and  one zone. Only the baseline has a minimum humidity schedule. Expected result: FAIL

standard.rule_description: Humidity Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.

rule-4-2-e.test_description: Baseline and Proposed building have one building segment and  one zone. Only the proposed has a minimum humidity schedule. Expected result: FAIL

standard.rule_description: Humidity Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.
